WEBVTT

00:00.283 --> 00:01.483
_

00:01.508 --> 00:03.575
- So how was your day off?
- I killed someone.

00:03.756 --> 00:05.756
Gail Rahimi, 42.

00:05.781 --> 00:07.546
Sickle cell disease.

00:07.957 --> 00:09.949
I thought you might need my phone.

00:09.974 --> 00:13.317
I'm a nurse. We were here
together the whole time.

00:13.352 --> 00:16.279
- And you are?
- Mary Harris. I used to work at Eden General.

00:16.303 --> 00:18.422
- Now, I work in hospice.
- Name of the hospice?

00:18.458 --> 00:21.181
- Joys.
- I admitted a new patient yesterday.

00:21.206 --> 00:23.360
- You must be...
- Lucy.

00:23.396 --> 00:25.959
- Desmond.
- Jesus, Jess. What happened?

00:25.984 --> 00:28.132
- Heather dumped me.
- To forget her...

00:28.167 --> 00:31.141
- you have to...
- Destroy her!

00:31.898 --> 00:35.897
- Run, dummy! You gotta run!
- We get a 911 last night.

00:35.922 --> 00:37.891
Guess who's on the scene?

00:37.916 --> 00:41.100
Dr. Mary Harris. The
angel of death herself.

00:41.125 --> 00:43.260
She's pregnant. Five months, maybe.

